---
description: Persistent agent memory -- read the Learnings section in AGENTS.md to avoid repeating past mistakes
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root before making changes. It contains rules, learnings, and role definitions for all agents.

When the user says "store this in learnings", "add this to memory", or similar, append the lesson to the appropriate category under the **Learnings** section in `AGENTS.md` using the format: `- **Short title** -- Explanation. (date)`
